          "en": "It was trapped! You take 10 damage.",
          "zh": "这是个陷阱！你受到10点伤害。"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": {
          "en": "Leave it alone",
          "zh": "不管它"
        },
        "effect_type": "nothing",
        "effect_value": 0,
        "result_text": {
          "en": "Better safe than sorry.",
          "zh": "小心驶得万年船。"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
